                Greeting-App
                ============
How to start
++++++++++++

Download the application image from https://hub.docker.com/r/auguysha11/greeting-app by either: 

running docker pull auguysha11/greeting-app && docker run -p ????:8080 auguysha11/greeting-app or 

docker run -p ????:8080 auguysha11/greeting-app. Replace the ???? with port a number of your choice.

When you start the container and navigate to http://localhost:8080 you should get a “Welcome to DevOps with Docker 2021!” as response.
